service.tut.pori.contentanalysis

Class ReferencePhotoList

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.tut.pori.http.ResponseData
      • service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.PhotoList
        • service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.ReferencePhotoList

  • public class ReferencePhotoList
extends PhotoList
    A special photo list used to list reference photos. In general, only a single photo is given as a reference for similarity search, but per the implementation of this class, multiple photos could be used as well.

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<referenceMediaList>
  <media>
    <UID>959cd699-3bc6-4d25-8723-35862e5c57d9</UID>
    <serviceId>6</serviceId>
    <mediaType>PHOTO</mediaType>
    <userId>4375607936430586469</userId>
    <url>http://fe.example.org/rest/carc/r?uid=959cd699-3bc6-4d25-8723-35862e5c57d9&amp;service_id=6</url>
  </media>
</referenceMediaList>
